<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 02:09:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>激光脉冲捕获未探索的极化子态</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/laser-pulses-capture-unexplored-polaronic-states</link><description>在一项国际实验中，研究人员观察到了贾恩-泰勒极化子——一种可能在未来超快自旋电子器件中发挥重要作用的准粒子。这些极化子出现在氧化钴晶格内，并被精心定制的激光脉冲激活。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/laser-pulses-capture-unexplored-polaronic-states.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 02:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/laser-pulses-capture-unexplored-polaronic-states</guid></item><item><title>Agentic AI 机器人帮助科学家与机器人对话，加快实验速度</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/agentic-ai-bot-helps-scientists-speak-to-robots-speeding-up-experiments</link><description>能源部西北太平洋国家实验室的研究人员使用大量自主机器人来设计和实施实验。然而，在自主实验室机器人上进行实验的速度却出奇地慢。这项工作需要科学家和工程师之间进行长时间的反复来设计实验步骤，这个过程可能需要数周时间。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/agentic-ai-bot-helps-scientists-speak-to-robots-speeding-up-experiments2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:54:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/agentic-ai-bot-helps-scientists-speak-to-robots-speeding-up-experiments</guid></item><item><title>无机纳米级设备的行为就像单个神经元，为人工智能和视网膜植入打开了大门</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/inorganic-nanoscale-device-behaves-like-a-single-neuron-opening-doors-for-ai-and-retinal-implants</link><description>麦吉尔大学的研究人员开发了一种光检测纳米级结构，可以模仿神经元处理信息的方式。类似神经元的行为来自于材料本身，减少了依赖电路或软件的类似设备的能源需求。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/inorganic-nanoscale-device-behaves-like-a-single-neuron-opening-doors-for-ai-and-retinal-implants2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:39:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/inorganic-nanoscale-device-behaves-like-a-single-neuron-opening-doors-for-ai-and-retinal-implants</guid></item><item><title>睡眠不足会增加人脑突触密度标记 SV2A 的水平</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/sleep-deprivation-increases-levels-of-the-synaptic-density-marker-sv2a-in-the-human-brain</link><description>突触稳态假说认为，睡眠对于通过缩小突触连接来恢复大脑平衡至关重要，突触连接在清醒期间逐渐加强和积累代谢成本。虽然之前仅得到临床前动物模型的支持，但最近的一项研究提供了人类这种机制的直接体内证据。研究人员对 40 名志愿者进行了评估，其中一半人经历了 28 小时的连续睡眠剥夺，利用正电子发射断层扫描 (PET) 来量化 SV2A 蛋白的水平，SV2A 蛋白是突触密度的可靠生物标志物。研究结果表明，长时间清醒会显着升高多个大脑区域的 SV2A 水平，尤其是海马体和丘脑。此外，在随后的两小时恢复睡眠期间，这些升高的 SV2A 水平与增强的慢波活动密切相关，慢波活动是深度睡眠和稳态睡眠压力的主要电生理标志。这些结果验证了人类突触稳态假说，证明了睡眠剥夺、神经连接积累和深度慢波睡眠的恢复驱动之间存在可测量的生物学联系。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sleep-deprivation-increases-levels-of-the-synaptic-density-marker-sv2a-in-the-human-brain2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:24:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/sleep-deprivation-increases-levels-of-the-synaptic-density-marker-sv2a-in-the-human-brain</guid></item><item><title>Anthropic 联合创始人：“我害怕我正在构建的技术”|剩下的就是政治</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/anthropic-co-founder-im-scared-of-the-technology-im-building-the-rest-is-politics</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/anthropic-co-founder-im-scared-of-the-technology-im-building-the-rest-is-politics</guid></item><item><title>Ben Goertzel 刚刚透露 AGI 何时真正实现 | EP。 38</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ben-goertzel-just-revealed-when-agi-will-actually-happen-ep-38</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:54:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ben-goertzel-just-revealed-when-agi-will-actually-happen-ep-38</guid></item><item><title>这是永不变老的关键吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/is-this-the-key-to-never-getting-old</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:39:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/is-this-the-key-to-never-getting-old</guid></item><item><title>糖衣纳米颗粒有望治疗最具侵袭性的脑癌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/sugar-coated-nanoparticles-show-promise-for-treating-most-aggressive-form-of-brain-cancer</link><description>俄勒冈州立大学的研究人员有可能找到一种新方法来治疗最具侵袭性的脑癌——胶质母细胞瘤，这种癌症的两年生存率低于 30%。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sugar-coated-nanoparticles-show-promise-for-treating-most-aggressive-form-of-brain-cancer.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:24:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/sugar-coated-nanoparticles-show-promise-for-treating-most-aggressive-form-of-brain-cancer</guid></item><item><title>玻尔兹曼熵的拓扑下界：通过质子锁相解决纯顶边界条件 (v.01)</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-topological-lower-bound-of-boltzmann-entropy-resolving-the-pure-top-boundary-condition-through-proton-phase-locking-v-01</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/the-topological-lower-bound-of-boltzmann-entropy-resolving-the-pure-top-boundary-condition-through-proton-phase-locking-v-01</guid></item><item><title>量子行政命令推进美国安全和创新</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/quantum-executive-orders-advance-us-security-innovation</link><description>经过&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-executive-orders-advance-us-security-innovation.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 23:54: